        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Yeon Ju is an elite prosecutor who started from the bottom. Although known as the best in corruption investigations for the Supreme Prosecutor’s Office, she suffers from amnesia after a car crash when chasing a suspect. As she wakes, she finds herself being Kang Mi Na, the daughter-in-law of the conglomerate Hanju Group. Before her disappearance, Mi Na was a troublemaker born out of wedlock.\n\nNow, sitting in her position, Yeon Ju\n\nis not able to hide her rough and outspoken nature. She then meets Seung Uk, a conglomerate who visits his first love, Mi Na, to reveal the truth of his father’s death. Will Yeon Ju and Mi Na be able to regain their lost memories in this mystery and succeed in true love?",
            "source": "asianwiki (Fallback: mydramalist)",
            "source_link": "https://mydramalist.com/683767-wonder-woman"
